name: EVO M
short_summary: Evo M module combines Microchip SAMD microcontroller with Intel MAX FPGA for enhanced embedded compute performance.
full_summary: The Evo M module by Alorium Technology integrates a Microchip SAMD microcontroller and an Intel MAX FPGA, offering a blend of performance and flexibility in an Adafruit Feather form factor. It supports IoT, Edge Analytics, and Motor Control applications.
full_product_description: Evo M is a compute module featuring a Microchip SAMD ARM Cortex-M microcontroller and Intel MAX FPGA. It includes analog inputs, outputs, digital IO, and external FLASH storage, designed for IoT and Edge Analytics applications.

name: HUMMINGBOARD PULSE
certifications: REACH, RoHS, ISO 9001, EMC/EMI Regulations, UL 94, Green/ Halogen Free
short_summary: HummingBoard Pulse with NXP iMXM Mini Quad-core ARM Cortex-A53, 2GB RAM, 16GB eMMC, and various connectivity options.
full_summary: The HummingBoard Pulse is a compact development board featuring an NXP iMXM Mini Quad-core ARM Cortex-A53 processor, 2GB of RAM, and 16GB of onboard eMMC storage. It supports Linux OS and offers a range of connectivity options including Ethernet, HDMI, MIPI CSI, MIPI DSI, PCIe, PoE, UART, USB, and USB OTG.
full_product_description: The HummingBoard Pulse is designed for commercial applications, powered by an NXP iMXM Mini Quad-core ARM Cortex-A53 processor. It includes 2GB of RAM and 16GB of eMMC storage. Connectivity options are extensive, featuring Ethernet, HDMI, MIPI CSI, MIPI DSI, PCIe, PoE, UART, USB, and USB OTG. The board supports Linux operating systems and operates within a temperature range of 0 to 70 degrees Celsius.
target_applications: Commercial applications requiring robust connectivity and processing power.

name: IMXM MINI SOM
io_count: ['USB, USB OTG, MIPI-CSI, UART, ESPI, I2C, SAI, SPDIF, GPIO']
certifications: REACH, RoHS, ISO 9001, EMC/EMI Regulations, UL 94
short_summary: iMXM Mini SOM with ARM Cortex cores and various I/O interfaces.
full_summary: The iMXM Mini SOM is a compact system on module featuring ARM Cortex cores, multiple I/O interfaces including USB, MIPI-CSI, and wireless capabilities such as WiFi and Bluetooth.
full_product_description: The iMXM Mini SOM by SolidRun is designed for developers and features ARM Cortex cores, a variety of I/O interfaces including USB, MIPI-CSI, UART, and wireless capabilities like WiFi and Bluetooth. It supports LPDDR memory and onboard storage options like NOR QSPI and eMMC.
